title: Zeyad Ishaish
text:
Zeyad Ishaish (; born 23 October 1998) is a Jordanian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%202020%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20welterweight">men's welterweight event</a> at the <a href="2020%20Summer%20Olympics">2020 Summer Olympics</a>. He was also the flagbearer for Jordan during the <a href="2020%20Summer%20Olympics%20Parade%20of%20Nations">Parade of Nations</a>.
His brother, <a href="Hussein%20Ishaish">Hussein</a>, is also a boxer.
